-- Monster fires suspended general counsel in probe
-- 
-- Wed Nov 22, 2006 8:51am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2006/11/22/us-services-monster-idUSWEN028120061122

 

 CHICAGO  (Reuters) - Monster Worldwide Inc. on Wednesday said its board fired the company's general counsel for cause related to its internal stock option investigation. 

 Monster, parent company of the leading jobs Web site, said it fired Myron Olesnyckyj, the former senior vice president, general counsel and secretary. He has been on suspension from his duties since September 19.